text: (Allahe arau udaharana diche) imaraanara jiyeka marayamara---- yiye nija lajjasthanara paraitrata raksa karaichila, phalata ami tata amara rauhara paraa phumraa'i dichilo arau te'om te'omra pratipalakara bani arau te'omra kitabasamuha satya buli grahana karaichila arau te'om achila anugatasakalara an'yatama
